See this page on classes and IDs.  As @naomipinkflower says, you’ll need (and probably want) to use one of the two to reference an individual element.
Alternatively, you have the option to style an element inline, by using the element style property.  For example:
<p style="color:white; text-align:center;">Hello, World!</p>

